snippet.title: Shaman: Spirithunter Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.shamanthegame.com/
Master your shapeshifting powers to break the Eternal Winter in “Shaman: Spirithunter”; a captivating VR adventure coming to Oculus Rift in 2018.
